  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.25,
    "endTime": 194.981,
    "text": "What countries did you go to?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.98,
    "endTime": 197.6,
    "text": "I have been to Korea, Japan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.62,
    "endTime": 199.0,
    "text": "I've been to Afghanistan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.213,
    "endTime": 205.0,
    "text": "I was in the airforce and I ended up getting Security Forces as my career field."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.0,
    "endTime": 208.401,
    "text": "Why did you want to be in the Marine Corp.?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.55,
    "endTime": 209.3,
    "text": "I wanted to be a pilot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.31,
    "endTime": 211.1,
    "text": "I wanted to be a military pilot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.2,
    "endTime": 212.69199999999998,
    "text": "Um, how is basic?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.3,
    "endTime": 217.5,
    "text": "For me, basic was very lonely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.78,
    "endTime": 223.1,
    "text": "So, getting a letter from my parents from home would take about two to three weeks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.17,
    "endTime": 227.29999999999998,
    "text": "So, when I saw everybody getting letters every other day, it was a little rough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.4,
    "endTime": 229.12300000000002,
    "text": "Dad, I'll write you letters every day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.3,
    "endTime": 230.8,
    "text": "I know, we have email now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.9,
    "endTime": 232.5,
    "text": "That makes it so much easier."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.6,
    "endTime": 235.5,
    "text": "My dad's deployed right now."
